1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 3=

3
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:08,200
Xuan.

4
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:13,719
You're here.

5
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:17,560
I woke up this morning
and saw your message from last night.

6
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:19,120
I rushed over without stopping.

7
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,599
Quick, feed me the gossip.

8
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,040
Why are you only wearing one sock?

9
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:28,040
I hurried this morning
and forgot the other one.

10
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:28,920
Never mind.

11
00:01:29,079 --> 00:01:30,640
Come on, let's gossip.

12
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:31,959
Slow down.

13
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:40,319
Simply put, Xiao Jin cheated.

14
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,680
I've called off our engagement.

15
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:46,120
He really is a scumbag.

16
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:49,560
Didn't you say before
that he seemed really dependable?

17
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:53,159
So he's really good
at putting on an act.

18
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:56,439
I'll make a voodoo doll of him.

19
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:58,799
I'll give out his number
at a men's health clinic.

20
00:01:58,799 --> 00:02:00,400
And I'll expose him on social media.

21
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:03,519
I've drawn a clear line between us.

22
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:05,680
But that's not what's bothering me.

23
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:08,680
What do you mean? Is there more tea?

24
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,168
I...

25
00:02:12,096 --> 00:02:13,479
I slept with Song Zhaoli.

26
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,159
Do you know Song Zhaoli?

27
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:17,120
Who?

28
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,960
Who in Qingcheng
doesn't know Song Zhaoli?

29
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:23,616
He's eccentric and jinxed.

30
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:26,560
He was even kidnapped
when he was in school.

31
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:29,479
And almost everyone in his family
passed away.

32
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,360
Only he and his grandfather are left.

33
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:35,159
Xuan, were you a moth in your past life?

34
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:37,360
Why do you
like playing with fire so much?

35
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,439
I didn't know it was him at first.

36
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:41,960
Unfortunately, he's also my client.

37
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,120
So what's his deal?

38
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,360
He keeps bringing up that night.

39
00:02:50,719 --> 00:02:53,759
West Lake Longjing tea?
Top-tier green tea behavior.

40
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:57,520
I have a feeling
he won't let you off easy.

41
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:08,439
(Miss Ji, we leave for the business trip
at 10 AM sharp tomorrow.)

42
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:23,479
Mr. Song, based on my observations
at the resort these past few days,

43
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:25,599
I suggest building the cabins
at these two locations.

44
00:03:36,448 --> 00:03:38,176
(Wedding Invitation)

45
00:03:38,439 --> 00:03:39,599
Won't you think it over?

46
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:42,719
If you're not satisfied,
I have two alternative proposals.

47
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,439
I'm talking about this.

48
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,120
He pushed you out to dance with me

49
00:03:57,479 --> 00:03:59,360
and made you
do a cross-arm toast with me.

50
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,039
He even stole your project.

51
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:03,919
Is a man like that worth trusting?

52
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,879
Mr. Song, this is between him and me.

53
00:04:09,159 --> 00:04:09,680
Alright.

54
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,159
Then let's talk about us.

55
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:15,240
That night, you had a boyfriend
and still slept with me.

56
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,160
Don't you owe me an explanation?

57
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,480
So what do you want?

58
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:24,160
That night I was with you.

59
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,040
Tonight you are with me.

60
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,439
Consider it even.

61
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:31,560
In what capacity
are you speaking to me now?

62
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,639
A client I can't offend?

63
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,680
You and I.

64
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,199
Man and woman.

65
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:59,639
Victim and perpetrator.

66
00:05:03,319 --> 00:05:04,000
Mr. Song,

67
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:07,360
after tonight, can you let me go?

68
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:10,399
From now on, let's only discuss work
and nothing else.

69
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,160
Okay.

70
00:05:13,399 --> 00:05:13,920
What time?

71
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,399
11 PM.

72
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,120
(Spelling it out makes it simpler.)

73
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:25,199
(Then let our relationship
be a short-term project execution)

74
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,680
(with risks controlled.)

75
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,800
What brings you here?

76
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:37,639
I'm the marketing manager.

77
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:39,240
I'm here to work with you.

78
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:43,000
That's just a nominal position.
Everyone knows it.

79
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:47,480
The position might be inflated,
but our engagement is very real.

80
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:48,720
Stop lying to yourself.

81
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,120
I don't like you.

82
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:52,199
This marriage isn't happening.

83
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:56,959
Zhaoli, feelings can be developed.

84
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:01,560
Besides, this engagement
was arranged by your grandfather.

85
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:03,000
You may run the Song Group,

86
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,079
but you can't override him.

87
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,079
Are you done?

88
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:09,519
Book her a separate room.

89
00:06:09,632 --> 00:06:10,240
Yes.

90
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:13,560
No need to trouble Mr. Qiu.
I can do it myself.

91
00:06:14,079 --> 00:06:16,199
Zhaoli, rest well tonight.

92
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:16,879
See you tomorrow.

93
00:06:24,279 --> 00:06:25,240
Look what you've done.

94
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:28,040
Miss Xie used her status
as your fiancée to pressure me.

95
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:31,040
I'm low-ranking and powerless to argue.

96
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,600
What else did you reveal about me?

97
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:36,040
Aside from Miss Xie
asking about your schedule,

98
00:06:36,319 --> 00:06:39,279
only Miss Ji asked me
for past reference plans.

99
00:06:39,519 --> 00:06:40,399
I've sent them to her.

100
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,839
Give me your phone.

101
00:06:41,888 --> 00:06:42,464
Okay.

102
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,208
Here.

103
00:06:50,688 --> 00:06:52,416
(Ji Xuan)

104
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,040
Register a new account.

105
00:06:54,759 --> 00:06:55,560
I'm taking this one.

106
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,879
As punishment
for leaking my whereabouts.

107
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,279
This account is mine now.

108
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,000
Any problem?

109
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:02,759
No problem.

110
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:03,959
No problem.

111
00:07:07,232 --> 00:07:11,328
(Wanda Vista Hotel)

112
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:09,600
Miss Ji, you look sexy.

113
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,639
Make it quick.

114
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:28,520
♪I didn't tell you then♪

115
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:32,000
♪Because I was afraid♪

116
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:35,200
♪You might not understand♪

117
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,920
♪You might've walked away♪

118
00:08:40,160 --> 00:08:42,680
♪But time has flown by♪

119
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:46,000
♪And you're still here♪

120
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:50,000
♪Still here with me♪

121
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:53,024
♪Forever irreality♪

122
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,039
Can't handle it already?

123
00:09:22,519 --> 00:09:23,519
What will you do later?

124
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:25,519
Just this once.

125
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:32,240
Ji Xuan, I said one night.

126
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:34,519
Not once.

127
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:42,360
♪But I think love has changed me♪

128
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:47,240
♪I'm here with you, I'm here with you♪

129
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:53,120
♪I'm here with you♪

130
00:09:53,344 --> 00:09:56,320
♪I'm here with you♪

131
00:09:56,480 --> 00:10:04,160
♪I can finally speak my heart♪

132
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:57,039
(Liao)
(Song, I remember who Ji Xuan is.)

133
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,279
(You're playing some cultivation game?)

134
00:12:28,308 --> 00:12:30,100
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

135
00:12:30,260 --> 00:12:32,140
♪Flickering neon lights♪

136
00:12:32,340 --> 00:12:35,668
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

137
00:12:36,180 --> 00:12:38,452
♪Every star is♪

138
00:12:38,740 --> 00:12:42,612
♪My heartbeat for you♪

139
00:12:43,924 --> 00:12:45,748
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

140
00:12:45,908 --> 00:12:47,460
♪And land in your arms♪

141
00:12:47,860 --> 00:12:51,316
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

142
00:12:51,572 --> 00:12:54,132
♪In the blue sky♪

143
00:12:54,196 --> 00:12:58,324
♪Your smile still lingers♪

144
00:12:59,252 --> 00:13:02,900
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

145
00:13:03,156 --> 00:13:06,820
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

146
00:13:07,028 --> 00:13:09,760
♪Can't find a cure♪

147
00:13:09,940 --> 00:13:14,644
♪To love you after we've parted♪

148
00:13:14,644 --> 00:13:18,676
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

149
00:13:18,676 --> 00:13:22,272
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

150
00:13:22,432 --> 00:13:24,340
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

151
00:13:24,436 --> 00:13:29,588
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

152
00:13:30,228 --> 00:13:33,940
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

153
00:13:34,132 --> 00:13:36,884
♪Can't find a cure♪

154
00:13:37,012 --> 00:13:41,652
♪To love you after we've parted♪

155
00:13:41,820 --> 00:13:45,588
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

156
00:13:45,812 --> 00:13:49,396
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

157
00:13:49,620 --> 00:13:51,424
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

158
